<div class="content"><nav aria-label="Breadcrumb" class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a> › Fleet Wraps Chicago</nav><h1>Fleet Wraps in Chicago</h1><p class="lead speakable">Chicago Fleet Wraps is Chicago's leading fleet wrap company — designing and installing consistent, professional vehicle graphics across fleets of 3 to 50+ vehicles. We wrap cargo vans, box trucks, sprinter vans, pickup trucks, and specialty vehicles for contractors, service companies, and enterprise fleets. Volume discounts up to 15%. Free pickup and delivery across Chicagoland. 2-year workmanship warranty on every wrap.</p><div class="cta-bar"><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/estimate/">Get a Fleet Quote →</a><a class="btn" href="tel:+13125971286" style="border-color:var(--gold);color:var(--gold)">📞 Call Now</a></div><div class="trust"><span>📅 <strong>24+ Years</strong> in Business</span><span>🏆 <strong>9,400+</strong> Vehicles Wrapped</span><span>✅ <strong>Avery Dennison &amp; 3M</strong> Certified</span><span>🚐 <strong>Free Fleet Pickup</strong></span><span>💰 <em>Volume Discounts</em> up to 15%</span></div><div aria-label="Common fleet wrap pain points addressed" id="service-pain-bar" role="note" style="background:#0a0a0a;border-top:1px solid #222;border-bottom:1px solid #222;padding:28px 0;margin:0 -24px"><div style="max-width:960px;margin:0 auto;display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:0;border-left:3px solid #FFD700;padding:0 24px"><div style="padding:0 28px;border-right:1px solid #222"><p style="font-family:monospace;font-size:.62rem;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#FFD700;margin-bottom:6px">Branding</p><p style="font-size:.88rem;color:#ccc;line-height:1.6">Unwrapped vans miss 40,000+ daily impressions in the neighborhoods you already serve. Every unmarked panel is your competitor's free advertisement.</p></div><div style="padding:0 28px;border-right:1px solid #222"><p style="font-family:monospace;font-size:.62rem;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#FFD700;margin-bottom:6px">Durability</p><p style="font-size:.88rem;color:#ccc;line-height:1.6">Cheap calendered vinyl fails in 12–18 months in Chicago winters. We use only Avery Dennison MPI 1105 cast vinyl — rated 5–7 years, zero paint damage claims in 10+ years.</p></div><div style="padding:0 0 0 28px"><p style="font-family:monospace;font-size:.62rem;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#FFD700;margin-bottom:6px">Cost Efficiency</p><p style="font-size:.88rem;color:#ccc;line-height:1.6">Wraps are IRS Section 179 advertising expenses — 100% deductible year one. A $3,750 cargo van wrap costs ~$2,700 after tax at the 28% bracket. Fleet discounts up to 15%.</p></div></div></div><img alt="Fleet wrapped vans for Frontier company in Chicago" loading="lazy" src="/images/frontier_fleet_vans.webp" style="width:100%;border-radius:8px;margin:0 0 24px"/><h2>Who Needs Fleet Wraps in Chicago?</h2><p class="body-text">Any business with multiple vehicles on the road benefits from fleet wraps. Your vehicles are already covering the miles — fleet wraps turn every mile into a marketing impression at just $0.04–$0.07 per thousand views. That's 100x cheaper than Google Ads and 50x cheaper than radio.</p><ul class="services"><li><strong><a href="/hvac/" style="color:var(--gold)">HVAC Companies</a></strong> — Service vans parked in driveways generate neighborhood-level brand awareness.</li><li><strong><a href="/plumber/" style="color:var(--gold)">Plumbing Companies</a></strong> — Branded vans build trust before the technician rings the doorbell.</li><li><strong><a href="/electric/" style="color:var(--gold)">Electricians</a></strong> — Professional wraps signal quality to homeowners choosing between contractors.</li><li><strong><a href="/contractor/" style="color:var(--gold)">General Contractors</a></strong> — Wrapped trucks at job sites advertise to the entire neighborhood.</li><li><strong><a href="/delivery/" style="color:var(--gold)">Delivery &amp; Logistics</a></strong> — High-mileage vehicles generate the most impressions per dollar.</li><li><strong><a href="/moving/" style="color:var(--gold)">Moving Companies</a></strong> — Box trucks are the largest mobile billboards on the road.</li></ul><h2>Benefits of Fleet Wraps for Service Businesses</h2><p class="body-text">Fleet wraps deliver measurable business outcomes that compound over time:</p><ul class="services"><li><strong>30,000–70,000+ Daily Impressions</strong> — Per vehicle, in metro Chicago traffic.</li><li><strong>$0.04 CPM vs $3.56 CPM</strong> — Fleet wraps cost 89x less than digital advertising per impression.</li><li><strong>2,500%+ ROI Over 5 Years</strong> — A $3,500 wrap generates millions of impressions over its lifespan.</li><li><em>Increased Trust &amp; Close Rates</em> — Customers prefer branded companies over unmarked competitors.</li><li><strong>100% Tax Deductible</strong> — Full wrap cost deductible under IRS Section 179 in the year of installation.</li><li><strong>Paint Protection</strong> — Vinyl wraps protect factory paint from UV, scratches, and road debris.</li></ul><h2>Fleet Wrap Rollout Process</h2><p class="body-text">Our fleet rollout process is designed to minimize vehicle downtime while ensuring brand consistency across your entire fleet:</p><ul class="services"><li><strong>1. Fleet Assessment</strong> — We inventory your vehicles by make, model, and year to create accurate templates.</li><li><strong>2. Design &amp; Brand Standards</strong> — We create a master design template that works across all vehicle types.</li><li><strong>3. Client Approval</strong> — Full-color mockups on every vehicle type before production begins.</li><li><strong>4. Phased Installation</strong> — We wrap 1–3 vehicles at a time so your fleet stays operational.</li><li><strong>5. Quality Control</strong> — Multi-point inspection on every vehicle before release.</li><li><strong>6. Ongoing Support</strong> — Replacement wraps for new vehicles and damage repairs.</li></ul><h2>Materials &amp; Durability</h2><p class="body-text">We use only premium cast vinyl rated for Chicago's extreme climate — from -10°F winter lows to 95°F+ summer highs:</p><ul class="services"><li><strong>Avery Dennison MPI 1105</strong> — 7+ year rated cast vinyl with Supreme Wrapping Film overlaminate.</li><li><strong>3M IJ180-CV3</strong> — Controltac cast vinyl with 3M 8518 overlaminate, 5–7 year durability.</li></ul><p class="body-text">Both materials are <strong>non-damaging to paint</strong> and can be cleanly removed at the end of their life or when you rebrand.</p><h2>Fleet Wrap Pricing &amp; Discounts</h2><table class="pricing-table"><tr><th>Vehicle Type</th><th>Per Vehicle</th><th>5+ Fleet Price</th></tr><tr><td>Cargo Van</td><td>$2,800 – $4,500</td><td>$2,520 – $4,050</td></tr><tr><td>Sprinter Van</td><td>$3,500 – $5,200</td><td>$3,150 – $4,680</td></tr><tr><td>Box Truck (16–22 ft)</td><td>$4,200 – $7,500</td><td>$3,780 – $6,750</td></tr><tr><td>Box Truck (24–26 ft)</td><td>$7,000 – $10,000</td><td>$6,300 – $9,000</td></tr><tr><td>Pickup Truck</td><td>$2,200 – $3,800</td><td>$1,980 – $3,420</td></tr></table><div class="pricing-cta-row" style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:14px 20px;background:rgba(255,215,0,.04);border-left:3px solid #FFD700;border-bottom:1px solid #1e1e1e;gap:16px"><p style="font-family:monospace;font-size:.72rem;color:#888;letter-spacing:.06em">Free estimate response within 2 hours · Free fleet pickup included</p><a href="/estimate/?vehicle=cargo-van" style="display:inline-block;background:#FFD700;color:#000;font-family:monospace;font-size:.68rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:10px 22px;text-decoration:none;white-space:nowrap;flex-shrink:0">Get My Cargo Van Estimate →</a></div><div class="pricing-cta-row" style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:14px 20px;background:rgba(255,215,0,.04);border-left:3px solid #FFD700;